  <bioghist id="aspace_12c65c07bc4bbb2d0009cb23f6bb7fb9">
    <head>Biographical Note</head>
<p>Daniel Katz is a labor historian and educator, teaching at the Murphy Institute of the City University of New York. A former union organizer, he is a member of the Board of Directors of Jews for Racial and Economic Justice in New York City.</p>  </bioghist>
